Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无垠的时间停止心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人无声息地自燃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界异常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之火笼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找的就是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.72,0:01:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被夺走之前先破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:01:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护秘器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不知道该怎么做...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇曳之炎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“星黎殿”还没有动静
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子遇到那个“秘器”坂井悠二之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直困扰于我们在“天道宫”没指点过她的感情中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被从未遇到过的无法自控的感情...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么对区区一个“秘器”...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的问题 万状饰者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们虽然没教给她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但应该深有体会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 对于这个孩子来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却对那个难以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以焦躁心急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 火雾战士的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不能因此而动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承“炎发灼眼的讨伐者”这一称号的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就更不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些这个孩子也都懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才困扰不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些徒想把坂井怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:06:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要坂井体内的“零时迷子”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那些家伙难道是要杀了坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 会把他救出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他还有谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井和那个火雾战士也想要杀坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐留下来的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐一只手就能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们连拿都拿不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和由佳里她们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和坂井同学也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学被掳走的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由佳里同学在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却只能看着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.26,0:07:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在说有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有靠我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你真的认为能救出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我们是因为大姐不在了所以死撑着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是由佳里同学和坂井同学的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:08:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近了也到不了他们身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗 赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“零时迷子”若是能满足我的所求...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无谓的担心你要担到什么时候 千变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫卡特将用存在之力成就永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在担心“成就”这一行为本身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是让我冰清玉洁的赫卡特多费手脚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说冰清玉洁对于“灵魂殿堂”而言十分重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“零时迷子”差不多也应该准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是什么地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会来这种地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙仍在“星黎殿”那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道“化装舞会”想利用“零时迷子”干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人蹊跷的是“悖论裁决者”的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔菲戈的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说这里将成为存在之泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在之泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“零时迷子”的特性是每晚复原存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用秘器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是“零时迷子”所能复原的只是当天失去的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到秘器本身有限的容量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是微不足道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是没必要那么兴师动众...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该存在什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到零点了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像忘记了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时迷子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫卡特 你想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能满足你的东西——零时迷子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去合并容器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合并容器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的赫卡特和那种秘器...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不正是赫卡特的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都无法模仿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“顶座”赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开容器 来我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正四散开来...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充沛我全身的无穷的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“零时迷子”肯定也很吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和秘器同化的赫卡特是如此地海量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无边无际
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像妖怪一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不满足
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不受影响
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰清玉洁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之因此“零时迷子”必须涌出难以置信的存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而“追根究底”的装置能将恢复的存在之力即刻抽取
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论过多久 容器都是空的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“零时迷子”将永远不停地恢复力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽取出来的存在之力从“星黎殿”中溢出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断充盈此地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不枯竭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同泉水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 存在之力？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时迷子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是“追根究底”的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 这个城市将集中大量的存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候 世界的平衡...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到事态进展得如此迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕没时间召集其他讨伐者了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能靠现在在这里的我们两个阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲入敌营
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过破坏秘器...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断绝那个装置的来源当然是获胜的有效手段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为火雾战士 绝对不能失败
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此 首先要治愈伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想让我怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道夏娜你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是秘器 夏娜是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究还是要毁掉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却什么都说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把坂井悠二怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说 希望坂井悠二怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛乔里大姐留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和那些徒战斗是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想交给你就送过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个救出坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们想自己救他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底我们所能做的只有这么点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让坂井死掉 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们拜托的不是火雾战士 而是作为平井由佳里的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去玻璃坛那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许能够帮上些什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为平井由佳里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次有人类那样请求你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想的好像和佐藤他们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我并不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是由佳里同学你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能够自己去救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究还是坂井同学和由佳里同学靠得更近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和悠二...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信由佳里同学你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢一个人的心是不会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢坂井同学的由佳里同学是值得信任的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好静养的话只会拖延伤口的痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘器的破坏是当务之急
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由佳里同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和坂井同学一同回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是喜欢坂井同学的由佳里同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要将悠二...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座城市的一切都将成为存在的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去有人得到过这么多的存在之力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 本“悖论裁决者”将成为第一人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该忘记了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这就是秘器的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的记忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传入了我体内
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的路你自己选
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一冲进去就没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道现在必须要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了之后自然会找到答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一名火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:20:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲入
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜保护了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅只是一个秘器的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 正在充沛我的身心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘器的 人的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么地深沉而强烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和目前为止合并过的容器都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要将悠二...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到达这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由佳里同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.24,0:22:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么“化装舞会”的徒这么叽叽咕咕地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.38,0:22:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是被“星黎殿”清除出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.88,0:22:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说老鼠会跳离将要沉的船
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有个重家伙 但沉是不会沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是贝尔菲戈那个老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.72,0:22:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那些家伙行动的确异常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.04,0:22:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像对拜访者不屑一顾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.27,0:22:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去问问看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.65,0:22:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了容易沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先狠狠地揍一顿之后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.06,0:24:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于冲入“星黎殿”的夏娜和维尔赫米纳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.12,0:24:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“化装舞会”的陷阱困住了两人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.00,0:24:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法回头的最终决战于此刻开始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.95,0:24:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.88,0:24:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星黎殿内的战斗
